<div class="container py-5">
    <h2 class="text-center mb-4">Frequently Asked Questions (FAQs)</h2>

    <div class="accordion" id="faqAccordion">

        <!-- GENERAL FAQs -->
        <div class="accordion-item">
            <h2 class="accordion-header" id="faqGeneral1">
                <button class="accordion-button" type="button" data-bs-toggle="collapse" data-bs-target="#collapseGeneral1" aria-expanded="true" aria-controls="collapseGeneral1">
                    How do I log in to the system?
                </button>
            </h2>
            <div id="collapseGeneral1" class="accordion-collapse collapse show" aria-labelledby="faqGeneral1" data-bs-parent="#faqAccordion">
                <div class="accordion-body">
                    Use your ID and password to log in. If you forgot your password, you need to ask admin to reset it.
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>

        <div class="accordion-item">
            <h2 class="accordion-header" id="faqGeneral2">
                <button class="accordion-button collapsed" type="button" data-bs-toggle="collapse" data-bs-target="#collapseGeneral2" aria-expanded="false" aria-controls="collapseGeneral2">
                    How can I update my profile information?
                </button>
            </h2>
            <div id="collapseGeneral2" class="accordion-collapse collapse" aria-labelledby="faqGeneral2" data-bs-parent="#faqAccordion">
                <div class="accordion-body">
                    Go to the "My Profile" section in the system and edit your personal details. Doctors and staff can only update their own profiles, while Admins have full access.
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>

        <!-- ADMIN FAQs -->
        <h4 class="mt-4">Admin FAQs</h4>

        <div class="accordion-item">
            <h2 class="accordion-header" id="faqAdmin1">
                <button class="accordion-button collapsed" type="button" data-bs-toggle="collapse" data-bs-target="#collapseAdmin1" aria-expanded="false" aria-controls="collapseAdmin1">
                    How do I add, edit, or delete users?
                </button>
            </h2>
            <div id="collapseAdmin1" class="accordion-collapse collapse" aria-labelledby="faqAdmin1" data-bs-parent="#faqAccordion">
                <div class="accordion-body">
                    As an Admin, you can manage all users by navigating to the "User Management" section. From there, you can add, edit, or delete accounts.
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>

        <div class="accordion-item">
            <h2 class="accordion-header" id="faqAdmin2">
                <button class="accordion-button collapsed" type="button" data-bs-toggle="collapse" data-bs-target="#collapseAdmin2" aria-expanded="false" aria-controls="collapseAdmin2">
                    Can I modify appointments created by staff or doctors?
                </button>
            </h2>
            <div id="collapseAdmin2" class="accordion-collapse collapse" aria-labelledby="faqAdmin2" data-bs-parent="#faqAccordion">
                <div class="accordion-body">
                    Yes, Admins can modify or delete any appointment in the system, including those created by staff and doctors.
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>

        <!-- DOCTOR FAQs -->
        <h4 class="mt-4">Doctor FAQs</h4>

        <div class="accordion-item">
            <h2 class="accordion-header" id="faqDoctor1">
                <button class="accordion-button collapsed" type="button" data-bs-toggle="collapse" data-bs-target="#collapseDoctor1" aria-expanded="false" aria-controls="collapseDoctor1">
                    How can I update an appointment?
                </button>
            </h2>
            <div id="collapseDoctor1" class="accordion-collapse collapse" aria-labelledby="faqDoctor1" data-bs-parent="#faqAccordion">
                <div class="accordion-body">
                    Doctors can edit appointments they are assigned to by going to the "Appointments" section and selecting an appointment to update.
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>

        <div class="accordion-item">
            <h2 class="accordion-header" id="faqDoctor2">
                <button class="accordion-button collapsed" type="button" data-bs-toggle="collapse" data-bs-target="#collapseDoctor2" aria-expanded="false" aria-controls="collapseDoctor2">
                    Can I add new patients to the system?
                </button>
            </h2>
            <div id="collapseDoctor2" class="accordion-collapse collapse" aria-labelledby="faqDoctor2" data-bs-parent="#faqAccordion">
                <div class="accordion-body">
                    No, only staff or specialists can add new patients. However, doctors can update medical records for existing patients.
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>

        <div class="accordion-item">
            <h2 class="accordion-header" id="faqDoctor2">
                <button class="accordion-button collapsed" type="button" data-bs-toggle="collapse" data-bs-target="#collapseDoctor3" aria-expanded="false" aria-controls="collapseDoctor3">
                    Where can i see my patient appoinment?
                </button>
            </h2>
            <div id="collapseDoctor3" class="accordion-collapse collapse" aria-labelledby="faqDoctor3" data-bs-parent="#faqAccordion">
                <div class="accordion-body">
					You can only see your patient appointment in the "Appointments" section based on your account. 
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>

        <!-- STAFF/SPECIALIST FAQs -->
        <h4 class="mt-4">Staff & Specialist FAQs</h4>

        <div class="accordion-item">
            <h2 class="accordion-header" id="faqStaff1">
                <button class="accordion-button collapsed" type="button" data-bs-toggle="collapse" data-bs-target="#collapseStaff1" aria-expanded="false" aria-controls="collapseStaff1">
                    How do I add a new appointment?
                </button>
            </h2>
            <div id="collapseStaff1" class="accordion-collapse collapse" aria-labelledby="faqStaff1" data-bs-parent="#faqAccordion">
                <div class="accordion-body">
                    Staff and specialists can schedule new appointments by going to the "Appointments" section and filling in the required details.
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>

        <div class="accordion-item">
            <h2 class="accordion-header" id="faqStaff2">
                <button class="accordion-button collapsed" type="button" data-bs-toggle="collapse" data-bs-target="#collapseStaff2" aria-expanded="false" aria-controls="collapseStaff2">
                    How can I add a new patient to the system?
                </button>
            </h2>
            <div id="collapseStaff2" class="accordion-collapse collapse" aria-labelledby="faqStaff2" data-bs-parent="#faqAccordion">
                <div class="accordion-body">
                    Staff and specialists can add new patients by accessing the "Patient Management" section and entering their details.
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>

        <div class="accordion-item">
            <h2 class="accordion-header" id="faqStaff3">
                <button class="accordion-button collapsed" type="button" data-bs-toggle="collapse" data-bs-target="#collapseStaff3" aria-expanded="false" aria-controls="collapseStaff3">
                    Can I delete an appointment?
                </button>
            </h2>
            <div id="collapseStaff3" class="accordion-collapse collapse" aria-labelledby="faqStaff3" data-bs-parent="#faqAccordion">
                <div class="accordion-body">
                    Yes, staff and specialists can create appointments, and delete or modify them once they are set.
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>

    </div>
</div>